VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT getValue\s*\(\s*[^)]*\+|findValue\s*\(\s*[^)]*(?:request|param|getParameter)
WHEN EXPR MISSING:ESAPI\.encoder|AntiXss|sanitize|escapeHtml
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects OGNL expression evaluation with user-controlled input via the ValueStack.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for OGNL Expression Injection via Action Name.
